divs: Sighting Detailslaying in bed i can see out my window. The first object caught my eye. It was shimmering and kind of moving in its area. as i looked out the window i saw two other, but stationary, kinda of amber colored lights. they looked like stars. They all stayed there for about 45min maybe more.
